00:00:20.922 --> 00:00:23.423 position:19% line:83% align:start
-So, today is the day.
-Uh-huh!

00:00:23.457 --> 00:00:24.659 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'll catch up
with you later.

00:00:24.692 --> 00:00:25.092 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:00:25.994 --> 00:00:27.795 position:35% line:83% align:start
All right!
I'll see you later, Coach!

00:00:27.829 --> 00:00:29.062 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Bye, guys!

00:00:32.499 --> 00:00:33.968 position:24% line:83% align:start
Does he always take
the ball with him

00:00:34.002 --> 00:00:35.269 position:21% line:89% align:start
when he goes outside?

00:00:35.302 --> 00:00:35.670 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:00:36.470 --> 00:00:38.506 position:38% line:83% align:start
You know,
I've been wondering...

00:00:38.540 --> 00:00:39.541 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:00:39.574 --> 00:00:42.042 position:19% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa was supposed to
go to school in Shutetsu

00:00:42.075 --> 00:00:44.144 position:33% line:83% align:start
to be part of
their famous soccer team.

00:00:44.177 --> 00:00:46.681 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why the sudden
change of plans?

00:00:46.714 --> 00:00:47.649 position:19% line:89% align:start
He really insisted that

00:00:47.682 --> 00:00:50.050 position:13% line:83% align:start
he wanted to be transferred
to Nankatsu

00:00:50.083 --> 00:00:52.520 position:19% line:83% align:start
and it looks like he's
already making new friends.

00:00:52.554 --> 00:00:53.655 position:24% line:89% align:start
And on top of that,

00:00:53.688 --> 00:00:57.090 position:19% line:83% align:start
the great Roberto Hongo
is going to be coaching him.

00:00:57.124 --> 00:00:59.661 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm sure his dad
will be very happy.

00:00:59.694 --> 00:01:00.695 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:02:45.833 --> 00:02:46.834 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:02:59.814 --> 00:03:01.783 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Medical diagnosis report.</i>

00:03:09.891 --> 00:03:11.391 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Hey, Roberto!

00:03:11.425 --> 00:03:12.660 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you have the uniform
you wore

00:03:12.694 --> 00:03:14.696 position:24% line:83% align:start
when you played for
the Brazilian national team?

00:03:14.729 --> 00:03:15.530 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:03:15.563 --> 00:03:17.330 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I'd love to see
the uniform

00:03:17.364 --> 00:03:20.267 position:13% line:83% align:start
that you wore back then for
the national team, Roberto!

00:03:21.669 --> 00:03:22.670 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:03:25.238 --> 00:03:27.141 position:19% line:89% align:start
Whoa, this is so cool!

00:03:27.175 --> 00:03:28.275 position:35% line:89% align:start
Number 10!

00:03:28.910 --> 00:03:30.310 position:16% line:89% align:start
Have a look at this, Mom.

00:03:30.343 --> 00:03:31.813 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's the real thing!

00:03:31.846 --> 00:03:33.881 position:21% line:89% align:start
It looks really good.

00:03:33.915 --> 00:03:35.382 position:21% line:89% align:start
By the way, Roberto,

00:03:35.415 --> 00:03:37.618 position:19% line:83% align:start
you did wash it before
giving it to him?

00:03:37.652 --> 00:03:40.054 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
Of course, I washed it!

00:03:40.088 --> 00:03:42.023 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[chuckle]
-[Tsubasa] Robero!

00:03:42.056 --> 00:03:43.256 position:38% line:83% align:start
Someday,
I'll take on the world

00:03:43.290 --> 00:03:45.727 position:24% line:83% align:start
with the best team
anyone has ever seen.

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:48.295 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even Brazil won't stand
a chance against me.

00:03:48.328 --> 00:03:49.831 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] [chuckle]
There you go.

00:03:49.864 --> 00:03:52.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[Tsubasa] [chuckle]
-I'll never forget that.

00:03:52.133 --> 00:03:53.901 position:21% line:89% align:start
I know you can do it!

00:03:53.935 --> 00:03:56.671 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Okay!
-[chuckle]

00:03:59.807 --> 00:04:01.709 position:19% line:89% align:start
"The world", he says...

00:04:10.317 --> 00:04:11.619 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Nakano]
What?

00:04:11.652 --> 00:04:14.889 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did you just say that
the soccer club won a match?

00:04:14.922 --> 00:04:16.858 position:41% line:89% align:start
[laugh]

00:04:16.891 --> 00:04:19.060 position:13% line:83% align:start
How about you see the score
with your own eyes?

00:04:19.093 --> 00:04:20.895 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow, you're right!

00:04:20.928 --> 00:04:22.697 position:19% line:89% align:start
5-2 against Nishigaoka?

00:04:22.730 --> 00:04:23.497 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's awesome!

00:04:23.531 --> 00:04:25.499 position:27% line:83% align:start
How did your lame
soccer club

00:04:25.533 --> 00:04:27.300 position:13% line:89% align:start
manage to score five goals?

00:04:27.334 --> 00:04:30.872 position:38% line:83% align:start
[chuckle]
Well, thank you for asking.

00:04:30.905 --> 00:04:32.707 position:21% line:83% align:start
Our new club member,
Tsubasa,

00:04:32.740 --> 00:04:35.143 position:13% line:83% align:start
scored four of those goals
all by himself.

00:04:35.176 --> 00:04:36.778 position:33% line:83% align:start
What's more,
the one who scored

00:04:36.811 --> 00:04:39.714 position:19% line:83% align:start
the deciding fifth goal
was me! [chuckle]

00:04:39.747 --> 00:04:43.483 position:13% line:83% align:start
My head shot was literally
a perfect goal!

00:04:43.518 --> 00:04:45.385 position:27% line:83% align:start
It was thanks to
Tsubasa's cross,

00:04:45.418 --> 00:04:46.486 position:33% line:89% align:start
to be honest.

00:04:46.521 --> 00:04:48.089 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[Ryo] Uh...
-Just hold on a minute.

00:04:48.122 --> 00:04:49.657 position:24% line:83% align:start
Who is this Tsubasa
character?

00:04:49.690 --> 00:04:52.760 position:19% line:83% align:start
And when exactly did he
become a team member?

00:04:52.794 --> 00:04:53.828 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well, actually...

00:04:53.861 --> 00:04:56.296 position:19% line:83% align:start
We ran into each other
out of pure luck

00:04:56.329 --> 00:04:57.965 position:30% line:83% align:start
during our last
spring break.

00:04:57.999 --> 00:04:59.299 position:33% line:89% align:start
By pure luck?

00:04:59.332 --> 00:05:00.501 position:13% line:89% align:start
What're you talking about?

00:05:00.535 --> 00:05:02.335 position:30% line:83% align:start
Wait a second,
that means that

00:05:02.369 --> 00:05:04.038 position:27% line:83% align:start
if it weren't for
that Tsubasa guy,

00:05:04.071 --> 00:05:05.640 position:27% line:83% align:start
you wouldn't have
scored any goals?

00:05:05.673 --> 00:05:06.373 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:05:06.406 --> 00:05:08.109 position:35% line:83% align:start
One person
scoring four goals

00:05:08.142 --> 00:05:09.510 position:30% line:83% align:start
is even better
than a hat trick.

00:05:09.544 --> 00:05:12.547 position:21% line:83% align:start
Even Shutetsu doesn't
have someone like that.

00:05:12.580 --> 00:05:15.482 position:27% line:83% align:start
We have some news
that'll surprise you too.

00:05:15.516 --> 00:05:17.552 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our soccer club
now has a coach.

00:05:17.585 --> 00:05:19.687 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I nearly forgot.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.556 position:33% line:83% align:start
Our coach is
the former member

00:05:21.589 --> 00:05:23.524 position:27% line:83% align:start
of the Brazilian
national soccer team,

00:05:23.558 --> 00:05:26.194 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Roberto Hongo.
-What're you talking about?

00:05:26.227 --> 00:05:27.360 position:24% line:89% align:start
Isn't that awesome?

00:05:27.394 --> 00:05:29.496 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's an acquaintance
of Tsubasa.

00:05:29.530 --> 00:05:31.799 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just what kind of guy
is this Tsubasa character?

00:05:31.833 --> 00:05:33.868 position:21% line:89% align:start
Look, there he comes.

00:05:33.901 --> 00:05:34.902 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:05:39.607 --> 00:05:41.609 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Sanae]
Is that Tsubasa?

00:05:41.642 --> 00:05:43.711 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
Yeah, that's him.

00:05:43.744 --> 00:05:46.147 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why is he dribbling
the ball right now?

00:05:46.180 --> 00:05:47.315 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just as expected.

00:05:47.347 --> 00:05:49.449 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's been dribbling
all the way from home.

00:05:49.482 --> 00:05:50.885 position:19% line:89% align:start
All the way from home?

00:05:50.918 --> 00:05:52.452 position:19% line:89% align:start
He's always like that.

00:05:52.485 --> 00:05:55.056 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wherever he goes,
he keeps on dribbling.

00:05:55.089 --> 00:05:56.290 position:41% line:89% align:start
Whoa...

00:05:56.324 --> 00:05:57.592 position:19% line:89% align:start
He's really good at it.

00:05:57.625 --> 00:05:59.560 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Nakano] It must be true
he scored five goals.

00:05:59.594 --> 00:06:00.695 position:33% line:83% align:start
He looks like
the kind of guy

00:06:00.728 --> 00:06:03.297 position:33% line:83% align:start
who could do
something like that, right?

00:06:03.331 --> 00:06:05.365 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, I did score
one of them.

00:06:05.398 --> 00:06:07.367 position:13% line:89% align:start
He only got four goals in.

00:06:07.400 --> 00:06:10.137 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey, Tsubasa!

00:06:10.171 --> 00:06:11.639 position:24% line:89% align:start
Good morning, Ryo!

00:06:11.672 --> 00:06:12.673 position:35% line:89% align:start
What's up?

00:06:17.745 --> 00:06:19.814 position:27% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa Ozora...

00:06:21.515 --> 00:06:23.084 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is Tsubasa.

00:06:23.117 --> 00:06:24.719 position:16% line:89% align:start
He is your new classmate.

00:06:24.752 --> 00:06:26.621 position:19% line:83% align:start
Make sure you make him
feel welcomed.

00:06:26.654 --> 00:06:29.056 position:38% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa,
please intorduce yourself.

00:06:29.090 --> 00:06:30.925 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, what's up, guys?

00:06:30.958 --> 00:06:32.093 position:24% line:89% align:start
My name is Tsubasa!

00:06:33.361 --> 00:06:35.495 position:27% line:89% align:start
By the way, uh...

00:06:35.529 --> 00:06:39.634 position:27% line:83% align:start
why did you bring
a soccer ball to class?

00:06:39.667 --> 00:06:41.369 position:16% line:89% align:start
'Cuz it's my best friend.

00:06:41.401 --> 00:06:42.603 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:06:42.637 --> 00:06:44.471 position:19% line:83% align:start
-It's your best friend?
-Yeah!

00:06:44.505 --> 00:06:45.640 position:33% line:89% align:start
Guess what?!

00:06:45.673 --> 00:06:47.875 position:35% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa has
joined the soccer club!

00:06:47.909 --> 00:06:50.645 position:16% line:83% align:start
This year, our club will
be different from before.

00:06:50.678 --> 00:06:52.780 position:13% line:83% align:start
The inter-school tournament
is gonna be great!

00:06:52.813 --> 00:06:55.016 position:38% line:83% align:start
[chuckle]
Sanae, I'm trusting you

00:06:55.049 --> 00:06:56.517 position:21% line:83% align:start
with cheering us on.
Can you handle that?

00:06:56.550 --> 00:06:59.452 position:33% line:83% align:start
Isn't Tsubasa
the really awesome player?

00:06:59.486 --> 00:07:01.522 position:30% line:83% align:start
The rest of you
never won a single game.

00:07:01.555 --> 00:07:04.625 position:13% line:83% align:start
You're all just members of
the no-good soccer club.

00:07:04.659 --> 00:07:05.826 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
That's not true.

00:07:05.860 --> 00:07:06.861 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:07.728 --> 00:07:09.263 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yeah, until the tournament,

00:07:09.297 --> 00:07:10.463 position:21% line:89% align:start
if Ryo and the others

00:07:10.497 --> 00:07:12.465 position:21% line:83% align:start
become better friends
with the soccer ball,

00:07:12.499 --> 00:07:13.935 position:24% line:83% align:start
they'll get better
at soccer.

00:07:13.968 --> 00:07:15.803 position:19% line:89% align:start
Roberto said so, guys.

00:07:15.836 --> 00:07:17.972 position:24% line:83% align:start
He called the ball
his "best friend."

00:07:18.005 --> 00:07:18.739 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right!

00:07:19.607 --> 00:07:21.509 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let's all go see
the new soccer team

00:07:21.542 --> 00:07:23.411 position:19% line:83% align:start
practice after school,
you guys.

00:07:23.443 --> 00:07:25.478 position:35% line:83% align:start
-All right!
-Yeah!

00:07:25.513 --> 00:07:27.882 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
Well, let's get ready.

00:07:27.915 --> 00:07:30.151 position:21% line:83% align:start
The entrance ceremony
is about to begin.

00:07:31.484 --> 00:07:33.888 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Principal] Students of
Nankatsu Elementary,

00:07:33.921 --> 00:07:36.390 position:24% line:83% align:start
especially those in
the fourth and upper grades

00:07:36.424 --> 00:07:37.692 position:13% line:89% align:start
who are in a sports club...

00:07:38.659 --> 00:07:40.594 position:24% line:83% align:start
I know you are all
restlessly waiting for

00:07:40.628 --> 00:07:42.863 position:16% line:83% align:start
today's entrance ceremony
to end.

00:07:43.731 --> 00:07:45.032 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Principal]
From today on,

00:07:45.066 --> 00:07:47.034 position:19% line:83% align:start
you'll start practicing
in preparation for

00:07:47.068 --> 00:07:50.304 position:13% line:83% align:start
the inter-school tournament
with Shutetsu.

00:07:50.338 --> 00:07:51.706 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't slack off!

00:07:51.739 --> 00:07:52.707 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Yes, Coach!
-Yes, Coach!

00:07:52.740 --> 00:07:54.608 position:13% line:89% align:start
You guys have to work hard

00:07:54.642 --> 00:07:57.078 position:10% line:83% align:start
to win our third consecutive
inter-school tournament!

00:07:57.111 --> 00:07:58.980 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:07:59.013 --> 00:08:00.715 position:19% line:89% align:start
Listen up, kendo club!

00:08:00.748 --> 00:08:01.782 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[yelling]
-We must erase

00:08:01.816 --> 00:08:04.352 position:30% line:83% align:start
the humiliation
of last year.

00:08:04.385 --> 00:08:06.220 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't give up,
keep on running!

00:08:06.253 --> 00:08:08.522 position:13% line:83% align:start
The inter-school tournament
is around the corner.

00:08:08.556 --> 00:08:09.523 position:19% line:89% align:start
Let's keep on training!

00:08:10.558 --> 00:08:12.093 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narrator] <i>The inter-school</i>
 <i>tournament...</i>

00:08:12.126 --> 00:08:14.195 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's a sports festival</i>
 <i>where each club</i>

00:08:14.228 --> 00:08:16.664 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>of the two elementary</i>
 <i>schools of this town,</i>

00:08:16.697 --> 00:08:19.867 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu Elementary</i>
 <i>and Shutetsu Elementary,</i>

00:08:19.900 --> 00:08:21.669 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>compete during a whole day.</i>

00:08:21.702 --> 00:08:24.271 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>On the eve of</i>
 <i>the 26th tournament,</i>

00:08:24.305 --> 00:08:28.209 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu has 12 victories,</i>
 <i>12 losses and a draw.</i>

00:08:28.242 --> 00:08:29.944 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's a perfect tie.</i>

00:08:31.512 --> 00:08:32.646 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Go Nankatsu!</i>

00:08:32.680 --> 00:08:34.815 position:38% line:83% align:start
One, two!
One two!

00:08:34.849 --> 00:08:37.785 position:16% line:83% align:start
This year, we'll finally
be able to settle the score.

00:08:37.818 --> 00:08:40.388 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's no wonder that
each club is fired up.

00:08:40.421 --> 00:08:41.822 position:16% line:89% align:start
Isn't that right, Sanae?

00:08:41.856 --> 00:08:42.757 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:08:42.790 --> 00:08:45.726 position:24% line:83% align:start
The biggest problem
is the soccer club.

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:48.629 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let's go and check out
just how good Tsubasa is.

00:08:48.662 --> 00:08:51.565 position:21% line:83% align:start
All right, we're off
to the soccer field, guys!

00:08:51.599 --> 00:08:52.800 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

00:08:57.738 --> 00:09:01.709 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh my, Roberto left
his jersey out here.

00:09:01.742 --> 00:09:04.945 position:16% line:89% align:start
Ace striker, number 10...

00:09:04.979 --> 00:09:06.047 position:30% line:89% align:start
Roberto Hongo.

00:09:07.081 --> 00:09:10.985 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's not Tsubasa,
but that's still very cool.

00:09:11.018 --> 00:09:13.554 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, I need to clean.

00:09:16.991 --> 00:09:18.859 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh! Oh no!

00:09:20.529 --> 00:09:21.729 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:23.697 --> 00:09:25.132 position:30% line:89% align:start
Medical report?

00:09:27.601 --> 00:09:29.036 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, Roberto.

00:09:34.341 --> 00:09:35.342 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:35.876 --> 00:09:37.111 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:37.144 --> 00:09:38.813 position:21% line:89% align:start
What does this mean?

00:09:42.883 --> 00:09:43.784 position:35% line:89% align:start
Roberto...

00:09:44.318 --> 00:09:45.719 position:30% line:89% align:start
It can't be...

00:10:08.109 --> 00:10:10.044 position:19% line:89% align:start
The weather's so nice!

00:10:14.448 --> 00:10:16.050 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Dear Coach Joao...</i>

00:10:17.685 --> 00:10:20.187 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>After all, it was useless.</i>

00:10:20.221 --> 00:10:21.755 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I did everything I could</i>

00:10:21.789 --> 00:10:24.058 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and upon the advice</i>
 <i>of Captain Oozora,</i>

00:10:24.091 --> 00:10:27.027 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I've finally made it back</i>
 <i>to my homeland.</i>

00:10:27.061 --> 00:10:29.630 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yet, the diagnosis</i>
 <i>still says</i>

00:10:29.663 --> 00:10:32.733 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>that I have</i>
 <i>retinal detachment.</i>

00:10:32.766 --> 00:10:35.136 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's true that</i>
 <i>we were late to notice it.</i>

