00:13:10.291 --> 00:13:11.892 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh? Hmm...

00:13:14.596 --> 00:13:15.796 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay!

00:13:15.829 --> 00:13:18.132 position:19% line:83% align:start
