I'm going to be
ready for them!

00:18:50.297 --> 00:18:52.299 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Nakano] That training
was really hard.

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:56.370 position:21% line:83% align:start
This Brazilian coach
really made them work hard.

00:18:56.403 --> 00:18:59.206 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm exhausted just
by looking at them.

00:18:59.239 --> 00:19:01.876 position:41% line:83% align:start
[yawn]
I'm exhausted!

00:19:01.909 --> 00:19:02.877 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:19:02.910 --> 00:19:06.179 position:35% line:83% align:start
Seriously?
You guys are so weak!

00:19:06.213 --> 00:19:08.181 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now what's your problem?

00:19:08.215 --> 00:19:09.383 position:27% line:89% align:start
Look at Tsubasa.

00:19:09.416 --> 00:19:11.151 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Sanae]
He still looks fresh.

00:19:12.352 --> 00:19:14.221 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
But he's not like us!

00:19:15.188 --> 00:19:16.423 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's no wonder everybody

00:19:16.456 --> 00:19:18.425 position:27% line:83% align:start
always makes fun
of you guys.

00:19:18.458 --> 00:19:21.129 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought you really wanted
the team to get better.

00:19:21.161 --> 00:19:22.329 position:35% line:89% align:start
Calm down.

00:19:22.362 --> 00:19:24.331 position:16% line:83% align:start
It'll take a lot of time
and practice.

00:19:24.364 --> 00:19:25.566 position:16% line:89% align:start
You've gotta be patient.

00:19:25.600 --> 00:19:26.668 position:27% line:89% align:start
I dunno if I can!

00:19:26.701 --> 00:19:29.137 position:19% line:83% align:start
Inter-school tournament
is about to start!

00:19:29.169 --> 00:19:31.105 position:33% line:83% align:start
You're right!
That's why...

00:19:31.139 --> 00:19:32.372 position:27% line:89% align:start
Remember, kids...

00:19:32.406 --> 00:19:34.876 position:21% line:83% align:start
you'll have to become
best friends with the ball

00:19:34.909 --> 00:19:37.045 position:24% line:83% align:start
if you want to win
your matches.

00:19:37.078 --> 00:19:39.113 position:27% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa and coach
are always telling us

00:19:39.147 --> 00:19:40.548 position:19% line:89% align:start
how important that is.

00:19:40.581 --> 00:19:43.350 position:27% line:83% align:start
How can we become
best friends with the ball?

00:19:43.383 --> 00:19:45.485 position:16% line:89% align:start
Always bring it with you.

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:48.221 position:10% line:83% align:start
You must remember to take it
everywhere you're going.

00:19:48.255 --> 00:19:51.025 position:13% line:83% align:start
At school, eating lunch...
Everywhere.

00:19:51.059 --> 00:19:52.225 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:19:52.259 --> 00:19:55.228 position:24% line:83% align:start
Isn't that how you
you always do it, Tsubasa?

00:19:55.262 --> 00:19:56.931 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, pretty much.

00:19:56.964 --> 00:19:58.298 position:33% line:83% align:start
You're always
dribbling the ball

00:19:58.331 --> 00:19:59.634 position:21% line:89% align:start
on the way to school?

00:19:59.667 --> 00:20:00.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:20:01.002 --> 00:20:02.235 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's right, guys.

00:20:02.269 --> 00:20:04.572 position:30% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa did not
learn that from me.

00:20:04.605 --> 00:20:07.742 position:16% line:83% align:start
He's been doing it since
he was a little boy.

00:20:07.775 --> 00:20:08.743 position:41% line:89% align:start
Whoa...

00:20:08.776 --> 00:20:11.546 position:33% line:83% align:start
From now on,
you can't use your hands.

00:20:11.579 --> 00:20:13.380 position:30% line:83% align:start
The soccer ball
does not appreciate it

00:20:13.413 --> 00:20:15.282 position:27% line:83% align:start
when you carry it
with your hands.

00:20:15.315 --> 00:20:16.584 position:30% line:89% align:start
Wait a minute!

00:20:16.617 --> 00:20:18.986 position:24% line:83% align:start
Are you telling me
we have to dribble the ball

00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:21.354 position:30% line:83% align:start
wherever we go,
like Tsubasa does?

00:20:21.388 --> 00:20:22.790 position:21% line:89% align:start
I know you can do it!

00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:24.959 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you have to!

00:20:24.992 --> 00:20:26.359 position:21% line:89% align:start
Easy for you to say!

00:20:26.393 --> 00:20:28.228 position:35% line:83% align:start
You want to
get better, right?

00:20:28.261 --> 00:20:30.363 position:13% line:83% align:start
What about the goalkeeper,
though?

00:20:30.397 --> 00:20:33.500 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hmm... I guess the same
goes for you,

00:20:33.534 --> 00:20:35.970 position:19% line:83% align:start
but sometimes, you can
use your hands too.

00:20:36.003 --> 00:20:37.071 position:35% line:89% align:start
Whoa, cool!

00:20:37.105 --> 00:20:38.405 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's not fair!

00:20:38.438 --> 00:20:40.240 position:16% line:89% align:start
That'll be all for today.

00:20:40.273 --> 00:20:43.144 position:13% line:83% align:start
Guys! Make sure you go home
dribbling the ball!

00:20:43.177 --> 00:20:45.113 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Are you serious?!
-Are you serious?!

00:20:45.146 --> 00:20:45.980 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Ryo] Yeah!

00:20:46.814 --> 00:20:48.516 position:19% line:89% align:start
See you later, Tsubasa.

00:20:48.549 --> 00:20:51.251 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hey, see you tomorrow, guys!

00:20:51.284 --> 00:20:53.020 position:33% line:83% align:start
Why don't you
cool it a little?!

00:20:53.054 --> 00:20:54.287 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Please don't embarrass us

00:20:54.321 --> 00:20:55.590 position:21% line:89% align:start
in front of Tsubasa!

00:20:55.623 --> 00:20:58.025 position:41% line:83% align:start
[growl]
Be quiet already!

00:20:58.059 --> 00:21:00.128 position:27% line:83% align:start
That looks really
difficult for them.

00:21:00.161 --> 00:21:01.929 position:19% line:89% align:start
These guys are awful...

00:21:01.963 --> 00:21:05.298 position:19% line:83% align:start
I know, but that's how
they're gonna get better.

00:21:05.332 --> 00:21:07.168 position:21% line:89% align:start
This is so exciting!

00:21:07.201 --> 00:21:08.536 position:33% line:83% align:start
I can't wait
'till the start of

00:21:08.569 --> 00:21:10.037 position:10% line:89% align:start
the inter-school tournament!

00:21:11.338 --> 00:21:13.273 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:21:13.306 --> 00:21:16.144 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm starving!
I need to get home quickly.

00:21:16.177 --> 00:21:18.045 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Tsuyoshi] Oh no!
-Huh?

00:21:18.079 --> 00:21:19.312 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just my luck!

00:21:19.346 --> 00:21:21.215 position:30% line:83% align:start
What am I going
to do now, Ryo?

00:21:21.249 --> 00:21:22.750 position:24% line:89% align:start
Aw, what a mess...

00:21:22.784 --> 00:21:24.351 position:30% line:89% align:start
Huh? Hold on...

00:21:24.384 --> 00:21:26.020 position:35% line:83% align:start
Do you live
around here, Manabu?

00:21:26.053 --> 00:21:27.155 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not really,

00:21:27.188 --> 00:21:29.289 position:24% line:83% align:start
but my best friend
won't even listen to me!

00:21:29.322 --> 00:21:30.258 position:24% line:89% align:start
What am I gonna do?

00:21:30.290 --> 00:21:31.592 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:21:31.626 --> 00:21:34.996 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm not really sure if we
can make it home like this.

00:21:35.029 --> 00:21:37.364 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's cool to be goalkeeper!

00:21:42.302 --> 00:21:44.071 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>He's very good.</i>

00:21:44.105 --> 00:21:45.840 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>As good as when</i>
 <i>I was his age.</i>

00:21:46.674 --> 00:21:49.610 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
 <i>No... Maybe even more.</i>

00:21:52.146 --> 00:21:53.247 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
There you go!

00:21:53.281 --> 00:21:55.817 position:21% line:83% align:start
The ball hasn't even
touched the ground.

00:21:55.850 --> 00:21:57.985 position:33% line:83% align:start
Hey, Tsubasa,
do you like soccer?

00:21:58.019 --> 00:22:00.922 position:27% line:83% align:start
What a question.
Of course I do!

00:22:00.955 --> 00:22:02.023 position:38% line:89% align:start
Perfect!

00:22:02.056 --> 00:22:04.725 position:16% line:83% align:start
From now on, you have to
wake up at 5 a.m. to train.

00:22:04.759 --> 00:22:05.860 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:22:05.893 --> 00:22:09.063 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm going to teach you what
real Brazilian soccer is.

00:22:09.096 --> 00:22:11.032 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ah! All right.

00:22:13.835 --> 00:22:15.435 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Dear Coach Joao...</i>

00:22:15.468 --> 00:22:17.404 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>I've found</i>
 <i>a glimmer of light.</i>

00:22:17.437 --> 00:22:19.006 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>His name is Tsubasa.</i>

00:22:19.740 --> 00:22:22.310 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll take my chances on him.</i>

00:22:22.342 --> 00:22:24.679 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>He has a lot of potential.</i>

00:22:24.712 --> 00:22:27.281 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll make him</i>
 <i>a world-renowned player.</i>

00:22:27.315 --> 00:22:31.252 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>I know I've left the field,</i>
 <i>but soccer will always be...</i>

00:22:31.285 --> 00:22:33.054 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>a part of my life.</i>

